WEBVTT

STYLE
::cue {
font-size: 1em;
font-weight: bold;
color: #ffffff;
}

00:01:31.180 --> 00:01:34.700 line:80%
=Generation to Generation=

00:01:34.820 --> 00:01:37.740 line:80%
=Episode 16=

00:01:45.780 --> 00:01:46.730 line:80%
Miss Cai,

00:01:47.780 --> 00:01:49.060 line:80%
the Young Master isn't with you?

00:01:49.700 --> 00:01:51.570 line:80%
He's been locking himself in his room.

00:01:52.730 --> 00:01:53.650 line:80%
The Young Master...

00:01:57.820 --> 00:01:58.980 line:80%
What happened to him?

00:01:59.420 --> 00:02:00.633 line:80%
What did his mother do to him?

00:02:01.820 --> 00:02:02.980 line:80%
He didn't ask me to tell you.

00:02:03.090 --> 00:02:05.290 line:80%
He didn't ask you
not to tell me, either.

00:02:06.930 --> 00:02:08.090 line:80%
If you won't tell me,

00:02:08.090 --> 00:02:09.090 line:80%
I'll go ask Xing.

00:02:09.740 --> 00:02:10.580 line:80%
Wait.

00:02:13.650 --> 00:02:15.060 line:80%
It's not that she did something.

00:02:15.060 --> 00:02:16.650 line:80%
It's that she did nothing.

00:02:17.460 --> 00:02:18.536 line:80%
Unworthy of being a mother.

00:02:18.683 --> 00:02:19.680 line:80%
Back then, Nie Hengcheng,

00:02:19.690 --> 00:02:21.843 line:80%
to control the Young Lord,
the Young Master's father,

00:02:21.854 --> 00:02:22.723 line:80%
kept sending beauties

00:02:22.734 --> 00:02:24.060 line:80%
into the Young Lord's chambers.

00:02:24.060 --> 00:02:25.310 line:80%
But the Young Lord was upright

00:02:25.310 --> 00:02:26.340 line:80%
and rejected them all.

00:02:26.340 --> 00:02:27.860 line:80%
Only Sun Ruoshui,

00:02:28.200 --> 00:02:29.530 line:80%
the daughter of his master,

00:02:29.810 --> 00:02:31.170 line:80%
kept saying

00:02:31.860 --> 00:02:33.490 line:80%
she had nowhere to go.

00:02:33.490 --> 00:02:34.740 line:80%
He softened for a moment

00:02:34.740 --> 00:02:35.810 line:80%
and took her in.

00:02:35.810 --> 00:02:37.090 line:80%
But after she gained his favor,

00:02:37.090 --> 00:02:38.580 line:80%
she got involved

00:02:38.580 --> 00:02:40.370 line:80%
with Nie Zhe as well.

00:02:42.650 --> 00:02:43.810 line:80%
Playing both sides?

00:02:43.810 --> 00:02:44.780 line:80%
Exactly.

00:02:45.140 --> 00:02:46.410 line:80%
How despicable.

00:02:47.740 --> 00:02:48.620 line:80%
Here.

00:02:48.620 --> 00:02:49.460 line:80%
Wet your throat.

00:02:54.300 --> 00:02:55.486 line:80%
There's something even worse.

00:02:55.860 --> 00:02:57.140 line:80%
Sun Ruoshui,

00:02:57.140 --> 00:02:58.490 line:80%
to please Nie Zhe,

00:02:58.490 --> 00:02:59.340 line:80%
actually claimed

00:02:59.340 --> 00:03:00.210 line:80%
that the Young Master

00:03:00.210 --> 00:03:01.780 line:80%
was Nie Zhe's son.

00:03:01.780 --> 00:03:02.930 line:80%
Isn't that outrageous?

00:03:03.860 --> 00:03:06.930 line:80%
She trampled the Young Lord's dignity.

00:03:08.970 --> 00:03:11.530 line:80%
Even worse than the stories in novels.

00:03:12.060 --> 00:03:13.490 line:80%
The Young Lord was so poor.

00:03:15.060 --> 00:03:16.370 line:80%
Everyone said

00:03:16.370 --> 00:03:17.970 line:80%
his wife cheated on him.

00:03:22.960 --> 00:03:23.810 line:80%
Fortunately,

00:03:23.810 --> 00:03:25.210 line:80%
heaven has eyes.

00:03:25.210 --> 00:03:26.330 line:80%
As the Young Master grew up,

00:03:26.543 --> 00:03:27.799 line:80%
he looked like his real father.

00:03:27.810 --> 00:03:28.690 line:80%
They looked

00:03:28.690 --> 00:03:30.580 line:80%
very much alike.

00:03:31.180 --> 00:03:33.060 line:80%
Only then did those rumors fade away.

00:03:33.060 --> 00:03:33.900 line:80%
So,

00:03:34.210 --> 00:03:35.180 line:80%
the Young Master

00:03:35.620 --> 00:03:37.210 line:80%
is truly the Young Lord's son.

00:03:41.690 --> 00:03:42.740 line:80%
Guanyue,

00:03:43.020 --> 00:03:44.460 line:80%
we're just talking here.

00:03:45.410 --> 00:03:46.580 line:80%
Can you stop forcing tears?

00:03:46.580 --> 00:03:47.490 line:80%
It looks fake.

00:03:48.140 --> 00:03:49.780 line:80%
This is all genuine emotion.

00:03:50.930 --> 00:03:51.900 line:80%
Don't fool me.

00:03:52.300 --> 00:03:53.690 line:80%
I grew up watching operas.

00:03:54.020 --> 00:03:54.970 line:80%
Your acting is far worse

00:03:55.370 --> 00:03:57.410 line:80%
than the Young Master's mother.

00:04:02.690 --> 00:04:03.930 line:80%
Speak of the devil.

00:04:04.526 --> 00:04:05.926 line:80%
We shouldn't have talked about her.

00:04:10.060 --> 00:04:11.180 line:80%
Greetings, Lady Sun.

00:04:11.180 --> 00:04:13.530 line:80%
You have deep insight into operas.

00:04:14.180 --> 00:04:16.340 line:80%
A refined soul indeed.

00:04:16.340 --> 00:04:17.180 line:80%
You flatter me.

00:04:17.500 --> 00:04:19.020 line:80%
Lady Sun, your life is like a play.

00:04:19.226 --> 00:04:20.530 line:80%
You're quite fascinating as well.

00:04:32.020 --> 00:04:34.700 line:80%
Your room is truly unique

00:04:35.050 --> 00:04:36.050 line:80%
in its arrangement.

00:04:36.290 --> 00:04:37.170 line:80%
Much better

00:04:37.170 --> 00:04:39.090 line:80%
than my quarters.

00:04:39.090 --> 00:04:40.780 line:80%
Qingyan truly takes

00:04:40.780 --> 00:04:42.580 line:80%
good care of you.

00:04:42.580 --> 00:04:44.050 line:80%
After all, I never abandoned him.

00:04:45.290 --> 00:04:46.130 line:80%
Lady Sun, please.

00:04:49.460 --> 00:04:52.210 line:80%
Every mother loves her son.

00:04:53.170 --> 00:04:54.900 line:80%
But I'm a weak woman,

00:04:55.580 --> 00:04:57.090 line:80%
strictly watched by Nie Zhe,

00:04:57.700 --> 00:04:59.020 line:80%
with limited freedom.

00:04:59.900 --> 00:05:01.580 line:80%
I truly had no choice.

00:05:03.500 --> 00:05:04.500 line:80%
I understand.

00:05:05.700 --> 00:05:08.170 line:80%
Yet when Mu Qingyan was
about to attack Bliss Palace,

00:05:08.820 --> 00:05:10.460 line:80%
you conveniently regained your freedom.

00:05:11.050 --> 00:05:12.970 line:80%
Nie Zhe is so considerate.

00:05:19.140 --> 00:05:19.980 line:80%
Please have some tea.

00:05:31.020 --> 00:05:31.860 line:80%
Miss Cai,

00:05:32.820 --> 00:05:34.210 line:80%
we're on the same side.

00:05:34.530 --> 00:05:35.850 line:80%
Why be so distant?

00:05:36.580 --> 00:05:37.610 line:80%
I heard

00:05:37.610 --> 00:05:39.210 line:80%
you're Cai Pingshu's niece.

00:05:39.730 --> 00:05:40.900 line:80%
With your help,

00:05:40.900 --> 00:05:42.020 line:80%
Qingyan is truly fortunate.

00:05:42.730 --> 00:05:43.570 line:80%
However,

00:05:44.020 --> 00:05:45.340 line:80%
I'm very curious.

00:05:46.500 --> 00:05:48.050 line:80%
Why are you willing to help him?

00:05:48.650 --> 00:05:49.580 line:80%
Is there

00:05:50.020 --> 00:05:52.140 line:80%
some unknown connection

00:05:52.140 --> 00:05:54.140 line:80%
between Qingyan and the Six Sects?

00:05:55.940 --> 00:05:56.940 line:80%
As for connections,

00:05:58.340 --> 00:05:59.180 line:80%
there are none.

00:05:59.380 --> 00:06:00.380 line:80%
But following my aunt,

00:06:00.780 --> 00:06:02.210 line:80%
I've always loved to right wrongs

00:06:02.210 --> 00:06:03.700 line:80%
and uphold justice,

00:06:03.700 --> 00:06:04.940 line:80%
especially when I see someone

00:06:04.940 --> 00:06:06.610 line:80%
bullied by their own mother.

00:06:09.020 --> 00:06:10.410 line:80%
Please drink your tea.

00:06:18.650 --> 00:06:19.780 line:80%
Miss Cai,

00:06:20.380 --> 00:06:22.140 line:80%
join me for this cup.

00:06:32.050 --> 00:06:33.290 line:80%
What exactly

00:06:33.290 --> 00:06:34.340 line:80%
are you here for?

00:06:35.140 --> 00:06:37.530 line:80%
There's no outcome between Nie Zhe
and Mu Qingyan yet.

00:06:37.900 --> 00:06:39.850 line:80%
Who will control the sect
is still uncertain.

00:06:40.780 --> 00:06:43.020 line:80%
For you to place your bet so early

00:06:43.780 --> 00:06:45.610 line:80%
isn't that a bit too eager?

00:06:45.850 --> 00:06:47.460 line:80%
Why misunderstand me so?

00:06:47.780 --> 00:06:49.700 line:80%
I truly want to help Qingyan.

00:06:50.050 --> 00:06:51.140 line:80%
Your suspicion

00:06:52.460 --> 00:06:54.050 line:80%
really breaks my heart.

00:06:56.170 --> 00:06:57.700 line:80%
How discourteous of me.

00:06:58.850 --> 00:07:01.460 line:80%
Since you harbor
so many doubts about me,

00:07:01.940 --> 00:07:03.460 line:80%
I shouldn't linger here.

00:07:03.820 --> 00:07:04.730 line:80%
Given time,

00:07:05.290 --> 00:07:07.050 line:80%
true intentions will be revealed.

00:07:25.050 --> 00:07:25.890 line:80%
Sleeping drug.

00:07:28.900 --> 00:07:30.610 line:80%
Poor acting, and childish.

00:07:31.497 --> 00:07:33.190 line:80%
Luckily, Mu Qingyan
didn't take after her.

00:07:33.820 --> 00:07:34.660 line:80%
Laxative?

00:07:35.210 --> 00:07:37.170 line:80%
Where did Mu Qingyan find
such a vile woman?

00:08:12.580 --> 00:08:13.780 line:80%
What are you doing here?

00:08:14.290 --> 00:08:15.210 line:80%
I can't sleep.

00:08:15.650 --> 00:08:16.500 line:80%
If you can't sleep,

00:08:17.460 --> 00:08:19.530 line:80%
go read or practice martial arts.

00:08:19.900 --> 00:08:21.170 line:80%
Or at worst, go perform a ritual.

00:08:21.580 --> 00:08:22.850 line:80%
Why come bother me?

00:08:24.380 --> 00:08:25.820 line:80%
I couldn't sleep,

00:08:25.820 --> 00:08:27.290 line:80%
so I wanted to chat with you,

00:08:27.290 --> 00:08:28.730 line:80%
but you were sleeping so soundly

00:08:28.730 --> 00:08:29.970 line:80%
that I didn't dare disturb you.

00:08:29.970 --> 00:08:31.210 line:80%
So, I lay down beside you

00:08:31.930 --> 00:08:33.220 line:80%
and waited for you to wake up.

00:08:33.220 --> 00:08:35.410 line:80%
Mu Qingyan, are you even human?

00:08:36.220 --> 00:08:37.060 line:80%
Compared to you,

00:08:37.740 --> 00:08:39.170 line:80%
those lechers killed by my aunt

00:08:39.170 --> 00:08:41.140 line:80%
were wrongly accused.

00:08:46.500 --> 00:08:48.050 line:80%
You've read so many stories.

00:08:49.050 --> 00:08:52.170 line:80%
Would those lechers

00:08:52.170 --> 00:08:53.650 line:80%
who sneak into a lady's room at night

00:08:54.170 --> 00:08:55.140 line:80%
lie there like me,

00:08:55.860 --> 00:08:57.740 line:80%
doing nothing at all?

00:08:58.930 --> 00:08:59.780 line:80%
Stay away from me.

00:09:08.100 --> 00:09:09.930 line:80%
You even brought a pillow?

00:09:10.810 --> 00:09:11.650 line:80%
Of course.

00:09:12.050 --> 00:09:13.900 line:80%
Doesn't that prove even more

00:09:13.900 --> 00:09:15.740 line:80%
that I'm not here
to do anything improper?

00:09:16.020 --> 00:09:16.860 line:80%
How so?

00:09:17.380 --> 00:09:19.050 line:80%
If I truly wanted to misbehave,

00:09:19.860 --> 00:09:21.050 line:80%
one pillow would be enough.

00:09:22.020 --> 00:09:22.726 line:80%
Besides,

00:09:22.786 --> 00:09:25.006 line:80%
I'm afraid you might harbor
improper thoughts about me.

00:09:25.380 --> 00:09:26.450 line:80%
You...

00:09:26.450 --> 00:09:27.380 line:80%
You're talking nonsense.

00:09:28.860 --> 00:09:30.020 line:80%
Say what you need to say.

00:09:30.450 --> 00:09:31.290 line:80%
Then leave.

00:09:32.410 --> 00:09:33.740 line:80%
I suddenly don't know what to say.

00:09:35.020 --> 00:09:35.930 line:80%
Zhao, you go first.

00:09:37.380 --> 00:09:39.100 line:80%
I went to see your mother yesterday.

00:09:40.310 --> 00:09:41.250 line:80%
What did you talk about?

00:09:41.930 --> 00:09:43.450 line:80%
She wanted to give me something.

00:09:44.100 --> 00:09:45.650 line:80%
I wanted to give her something too.

00:09:45.650 --> 00:09:46.530 line:80%
Give something?

00:09:48.020 --> 00:09:48.813 line:80%
What?

00:09:48.906 --> 00:09:50.032 line:80%
She gave me a sleeping drug.

00:09:50.450 --> 00:09:51.570 line:80%
I gave her a laxative.

00:09:54.570 --> 00:09:55.740 line:80%
In this whole world,

00:09:56.530 --> 00:09:58.050 line:80%
only you would deal with her like that.

00:09:58.740 --> 00:10:00.410 line:80%
Your father was such a detached man.

00:10:01.050 --> 00:10:02.620 line:80%
Why did he fall for her?

00:10:09.573 --> 00:10:11.100 line:80%
She was my father's master's daughter.

00:10:12.650 --> 00:10:14.170 line:80%
Nie Hengcheng brought her to him.

00:10:14.690 --> 00:10:15.620 line:80%
He knew my father

00:10:16.930 --> 00:10:17.770 line:80%
would soften

00:10:18.170 --> 00:10:19.450 line:80%
and take her in.

00:10:21.220 --> 00:10:22.570 line:80%
She was good at endurance.

00:10:23.500 --> 00:10:24.810 line:80%
She stayed for five or six years,

00:10:25.930 --> 00:10:27.100 line:80%
only discussing poetry,

00:10:28.780 --> 00:10:29.860 line:80%
never overstepping.

00:10:31.410 --> 00:10:32.330 line:80%
Over time,

00:10:33.570 --> 00:10:34.690 line:80%
feelings naturally grew.

00:10:35.410 --> 00:10:36.330 line:80%
Five or six years.

00:10:37.780 --> 00:10:39.620 line:80%
Nie Hengcheng was quite patient.

00:10:39.980 --> 00:10:41.410 line:80%
Nie Hengcheng excelled at schemes.

00:10:42.810 --> 00:10:44.330 line:80%
If he wanted something done,

00:10:44.930 --> 00:10:46.050 line:80%
he would wait for 10 years,

00:10:46.780 --> 00:10:48.050 line:80%
or even 20 years.

00:10:49.783 --> 00:10:51.330 line:80%
He longed for sole control of the sect

00:10:52.020 --> 00:10:53.380 line:80%
but feared public condemnation.

00:10:54.410 --> 00:10:55.330 line:80%
He never truly killed

00:10:55.900 --> 00:10:57.570 line:80%
the Mu clan descendants.

00:10:58.140 --> 00:10:59.500 line:80%
Instead, he manipulated them

00:11:00.530 --> 00:11:02.380 line:80%
and made them like puppets.

00:11:04.050 --> 00:11:05.050 line:80%
Through marriage,

00:11:05.132 --> 00:11:06.589 line:80%
he plotted against my grandparents,

00:11:06.661 --> 00:11:08.520 line:80%
turning them against each other
in middle age.

00:11:09.330 --> 00:11:10.345 line:80%
Their own flesh and blood

00:11:10.740 --> 00:11:11.985 line:80%
nearly died in a foreign land.

00:11:12.290 --> 00:11:13.130 line:80%
Later,

00:11:13.500 --> 00:11:14.570 line:80%
exploiting compassion

00:11:14.980 --> 00:11:15.930 line:80%
and a sense of duty,

00:11:16.170 --> 00:11:17.570 line:80%
he bound my father as well.

00:11:20.100 --> 00:11:21.140 line:80%
My poor father.

00:11:22.170 --> 00:11:24.570 line:80%
He longed for the outside world.

00:11:25.650 --> 00:11:26.780 line:80%
Yet in his lifetime,

00:11:28.330 --> 00:11:30.620 line:80%
he never once left the Hanhai Mountains.

00:11:41.930 --> 00:11:43.450 line:80%
Nie Hengcheng is dead.

00:11:44.650 --> 00:11:45.490 line:80%
Zhao,

00:11:46.980 --> 00:11:47.820 line:80%
all of this

00:11:48.810 --> 00:11:49.930 line:80%
will end very soon.

00:11:54.290 --> 00:11:55.130 line:80%
Mu Qingyan.

00:11:59.450 --> 00:12:00.290 line:80%
Young Master,

00:12:00.450 --> 00:12:01.490 line:80%
nothing can happen to you.

00:12:01.860 --> 00:12:02.700 line:80%
If you're gone,

00:12:02.710 --> 00:12:03.650 line:80%
what will we do?

00:12:03.780 --> 00:12:05.140 line:80%
Stop wailing like ghosts.

00:12:07.410 --> 00:12:08.250 line:80%
Qingyan.

00:12:09.650 --> 00:12:10.490 line:80%
Qingyan!

00:12:11.530 --> 00:12:12.370 line:80%
Qingyan.

00:12:18.170 --> 00:12:19.810 line:80%
Why do you treat Qingyan this way?

00:12:20.050 --> 00:12:20.930 line:80%
Did you

00:12:20.930 --> 00:12:22.290 line:80%
really poison him?

00:12:23.050 --> 00:12:24.410 line:80%
I was about to ask you.

00:12:24.780 --> 00:12:26.810 line:80%
He was fine when he attacked
Xuanwu Altar,

00:12:27.356 --> 00:12:28.810 line:80%
yet he was poisoned once you arrived.

00:12:28.810 --> 00:12:30.380 line:80%
I felt sorry for Qingyan.

00:12:32.170 --> 00:12:34.570 line:80%
Why would he be poisoned in your room?

00:12:34.570 --> 00:12:35.570 line:80%
If there were no cause,

00:12:35.570 --> 00:12:37.690 line:80%
why was he in your room at dawn?

00:12:37.690 --> 00:12:38.650 line:80%
What's wrong with that?

00:12:39.323 --> 00:12:40.632 line:80%
We've traveled and lived together

00:12:40.643 --> 00:12:41.780 line:80%
for months.

00:12:41.780 --> 00:12:43.290 line:80%
If I wanted to harm him,

00:12:43.290 --> 00:12:44.410 line:80%
I would've done it long ago.

00:12:44.980 --> 00:12:46.196 line:80%
Why wait until now?

00:12:46.276 --> 00:12:47.740 line:80%
I think you're shifting the suspicion.

00:12:48.140 --> 00:12:49.066 line:80%
Among everyone present,

00:12:49.450 --> 00:12:50.900 line:80%
you're the most suspicious.

00:12:52.590 --> 00:12:53.450 line:80%
Shangguan.

00:12:53.450 --> 00:12:54.290 line:80%
Yes.

00:12:54.450 --> 00:12:55.380 line:80%
Take her out.

00:12:56.980 --> 00:12:58.620 line:80%
Lady Sun, please.

00:12:58.620 --> 00:12:59.460 line:80%
Shangguan,

00:12:59.930 --> 00:13:01.410 line:80%
how dare you treat me like this?

00:13:03.380 --> 00:13:04.220 line:80%
Let go.

00:13:04.650 --> 00:13:05.490 line:80%
Qingyan.

00:13:05.930 --> 00:13:06.770 line:80%
Qingyan.

00:13:07.140 --> 00:13:07.980 line:80%
Qingyan.

00:13:08.120 --> 00:13:09.290 line:80%
- What a surprise.
- Qingyan.

00:13:09.330 --> 00:13:10.620 line:80%
Shangguan is quite formidable.

00:13:10.923 --> 00:13:13.109 line:80%
I need to give him a herbal bath
to dispel the poison.

00:13:13.740 --> 00:13:14.580 line:80%
Let's go.

00:13:14.860 --> 00:13:16.020 line:80%
Mr. Dai, let's go.

00:13:18.570 --> 00:13:19.930 line:80%
Poison changes are unpredictable.

00:13:20.980 --> 00:13:21.930 line:80%
Young Master, take care.

00:13:24.530 --> 00:13:26.323 line:80%
This is a Savior Pill
made by Guangtian Sect.

00:13:26.620 --> 00:13:27.500 line:80%
It may be useful.

00:13:36.570 --> 00:13:37.410 line:80%
She believed it?

00:13:38.810 --> 00:13:39.740 line:80%
She checked the pulse.

00:13:39.740 --> 00:13:40.650 line:80%
You watched the show.

00:13:41.410 --> 00:13:42.450 line:80%
She should believe it now.

00:13:44.410 --> 00:13:45.570 line:80%
How did she poison you?

00:13:48.810 --> 00:13:50.220 line:80%
My father's Fuying Sword.

00:13:50.860 --> 00:13:51.700 line:80%
She knew

00:13:52.050 --> 00:13:53.410 line:80%
I cared most about my father.

00:13:55.500 --> 00:13:56.570 line:80%
But it's fine.

00:13:57.860 --> 00:13:59.330 line:80%
I can use my inner power

00:13:59.740 --> 00:14:00.980 line:80%
to suppress the poison.

00:14:02.020 --> 00:14:04.260 line:80%
She must have acted
under Nie Zhe's orders.

00:14:12.530 --> 00:14:13.370 line:80%
Zhao,

00:14:14.810 --> 00:14:15.650 line:80%
are you willing

00:14:18.690 --> 00:14:20.290 line:80%
to know the real me?

00:14:28.570 --> 00:14:29.410 line:80%
This place

00:14:30.620 --> 00:14:31.930 line:80%
was my only world

00:14:33.100 --> 00:14:34.170 line:80%
before I turned five.

00:14:36.330 --> 00:14:37.370 line:80%
Not long after I was born,

00:14:37.810 --> 00:14:38.803 line:80%
my father was attacked;

00:14:39.050 --> 00:14:40.170 line:80%
his fate was unknown.

00:14:41.020 --> 00:14:42.100 line:80%
When I was one year old,

00:14:42.980 --> 00:14:44.810 line:80%
Nie Zhe, not yet the Chief,

00:14:44.810 --> 00:14:46.100 line:80%
severed my tendons,

00:14:48.500 --> 00:14:50.810 line:80%
forcing Sun Ruoshui to abandon me here.

00:15:08.530 --> 00:15:09.450 line:80%
The child is young.

00:15:09.860 --> 00:15:11.450 line:80%
His limbs will heal soon.

00:15:12.050 --> 00:15:13.020 line:80%
This place is quiet,

00:15:13.860 --> 00:15:15.570 line:80%
free from meddlesome people.

00:15:26.380 --> 00:15:27.530 line:80%
For five whole years,

00:15:29.020 --> 00:15:30.290 line:80%
I had been locked here,

00:15:31.140 --> 00:15:32.530 line:80%
never seeing daylight,

00:15:34.050 --> 00:15:35.930 line:80%
living like a beast.

00:15:59.650 --> 00:16:01.740 line:80%
He doesn't eat like a Young Master.

00:16:01.980 --> 00:16:02.930 line:80%
What a sin.

00:16:03.930 --> 00:16:04.770 line:80%
What do you know?

00:16:04.900 --> 00:16:06.500 line:80%
He's still a Mu.

00:16:06.500 --> 00:16:07.566 line:80%
Killing him would look bad.

00:16:08.290 --> 00:16:09.380 line:80%
With this going on,

00:16:09.740 --> 00:16:11.039 line:80%
he'll be useless sooner or later.

00:16:30.810 --> 00:16:31.740 line:80%
And then?

00:16:38.170 --> 00:16:39.810 line:80%
Later, my father recovered and returned.

00:16:40.450 --> 00:16:41.500 line:80%
When he learned I was here,

00:16:41.930 --> 00:16:43.140 line:80%
he took me back.

00:17:26.570 --> 00:17:27.740 line:80%
My tendons were severed.

00:17:28.660 --> 00:17:30.460 line:80%
My father exhausted his inner power

00:17:30.460 --> 00:17:31.740 line:80%
to rebuild my meridians.

00:17:32.810 --> 00:17:33.780 line:80%
Because of that,

00:17:34.660 --> 00:17:35.780 line:80%
he suffered internal injuries

00:17:36.530 --> 00:17:37.660 line:80%
and a lingering illness.

00:17:46.660 --> 00:17:47.570 line:80%
A few years ago,

00:17:48.700 --> 00:17:50.700 line:80%
my father reached the end of his life

00:17:51.500 --> 00:17:52.890 line:80%
and passed away.

00:17:53.890 --> 00:17:55.660 line:80%
My father's death was suspicious.

00:17:56.740 --> 00:17:58.320 line:80%
Elder Qiu told me how the Nies

00:17:58.331 --> 00:18:00.510 line:80%
(Spirit Tablet of Mu Zhengming)
persecuted my father,

00:18:00.521 --> 00:18:02.291 line:80%
as well as matters
involving my grandfather.

00:18:05.220 --> 00:18:06.530 line:80%
My hatred was unbearable.

00:18:07.020 --> 00:18:08.460 line:80%
I stormed Bliss Palace

00:18:09.460 --> 00:18:10.810 line:80%
to settle accounts with Nie Zhe.

00:18:42.330 --> 00:18:44.420 line:80%
Before, I thought Nie Zhe's Wudu Palm

00:18:45.090 --> 00:18:46.290 line:80%
was poisonous without a cure.

00:18:46.850 --> 00:18:47.780 line:80%
But I did not expect

00:18:48.066 --> 00:18:49.706 line:80%
Nie Zhe's cultivation
to be insufficient.

00:18:50.020 --> 00:18:51.220 line:80%
The Wudu Palm he practices

00:18:51.570 --> 00:18:52.980 line:80%
is not toxic enough to be fatal.

00:18:54.180 --> 00:18:55.130 line:80%
Was it your mother?

00:18:57.240 --> 00:18:58.380 line:80%
It was Nie Zhe.

00:18:58.570 --> 00:19:00.020 line:80%
Knowing that my father and I

00:19:00.020 --> 00:19:01.610 line:80%
both valued the Fuying Sword,

00:19:01.890 --> 00:19:04.330 line:80%
he instructed Sun Ruoshui
to poison the blade.

00:19:05.020 --> 00:19:07.890 line:80%
This time, Nie Zhe wanted
to repeat the trick.

00:19:08.660 --> 00:19:10.890 line:80%
That's how I confirmed my suspicion.

00:19:11.290 --> 00:19:13.136 line:80%
Nie Zhe was certain
you didn't know the truth,

00:19:13.370 --> 00:19:15.090 line:80%
so he poisoned the sword again,

00:19:15.090 --> 00:19:16.980 line:80%
trying to use your mother
to harm you once more.

00:19:19.500 --> 00:19:20.500 line:80%
What a fool.

00:19:20.780 --> 00:19:21.620 line:80%
She's not foolish.

00:19:23.370 --> 00:19:24.290 line:80%
She is arrogant.

00:19:24.890 --> 00:19:26.610 line:80%
My father indulged her in every way.

00:19:27.660 --> 00:19:29.090 line:80%
She thought I was like my father,

00:19:29.289 --> 00:19:30.762 line:80%
someone she could manipulate at will.

00:19:31.130 --> 00:19:32.780 line:80%
So I played along with her plan,

00:19:32.791 --> 00:19:34.664 line:80%
letting her return
to let down Nie Zhe's guard.

00:19:34.850 --> 00:19:36.130 line:80%
After taking Bliss Palace,

00:19:37.050 --> 00:19:38.130 line:80%
how will you deal with her?

00:19:38.610 --> 00:19:39.570 line:80%
I promised my father

00:19:40.850 --> 00:19:42.130 line:80%
to provide for her in old age.

00:19:43.530 --> 00:19:44.950 line:80%
So, I'll provide for her in old age.

00:19:45.570 --> 00:19:47.940 line:80%
After dealing with Nie Zhe
and his followers,

00:19:48.290 --> 00:19:51.050 line:80%
I'll find a clean, comfortable place
for her to live.

00:19:51.660 --> 00:19:53.180 line:80%
She'll live a good life.

00:19:53.180 --> 00:19:54.130 line:80%
No visitors.

00:19:55.660 --> 00:19:56.810 line:80%
She'll grow old in solitude.

00:19:57.180 --> 00:19:58.380 line:80%
Everything happens in circles.

00:19:58.570 --> 00:19:59.600 line:80%
Retribution always comes.

00:19:59.980 --> 00:20:01.020 line:80%
She deserves it.

00:20:02.700 --> 00:20:03.780 line:80%
I'm speaking objectively.

00:20:04.500 --> 00:20:05.500 line:80%
Don't overthink it.

00:20:05.500 --> 00:20:06.370 line:80%
I'm not overthinking.

00:20:07.330 --> 00:20:09.020 line:80%
I just feel that compared to me,

00:20:09.570 --> 00:20:11.220 line:80%
you're more like a demonic sect member.

00:20:11.220 --> 00:20:12.686 line:80%
I'm now an undercover agent

00:20:12.697 --> 00:20:14.230 line:80%
from the Six Sects in the demonic sect.

00:20:14.370 --> 00:20:15.700 line:80%
Naturally, I must act the part.

00:20:17.780 --> 00:20:18.940 line:80%
After dealing with Nie Zhe,

00:20:20.130 --> 00:20:20.970 line:80%
what are your plans?

00:20:22.810 --> 00:20:24.370 line:80%
My father's only regret in life

00:20:24.780 --> 00:20:26.530 line:80%
was never leaving the Hanhai Mountains.

00:20:26.980 --> 00:20:28.810 line:80%
Though I couldn't fulfill his wish,

00:20:29.320 --> 00:20:30.660 line:80%
I still want to follow his intent

00:20:31.290 --> 00:20:32.530 line:80%
and make the Hanhai Mountains

00:20:32.780 --> 00:20:34.810 line:80%
no longer a closed-off place.

00:20:35.500 --> 00:20:36.453 line:80%
To achieve great change,

00:20:36.876 --> 00:20:38.139 line:80%
one must first destroy greatly.

00:20:38.500 --> 00:20:39.570 line:80%
The sect's power

00:20:39.940 --> 00:20:41.290 line:80%
is deeply entangled.

00:20:41.290 --> 00:20:42.610 line:80%
Without absolute strength,

00:20:42.610 --> 00:20:44.220 line:80%
it's hard to win a submission quickly.

00:20:45.610 --> 00:20:46.530 line:80%
I don't have much time.

00:20:46.890 --> 00:20:47.980 line:80%
And I stand alone.

00:20:49.167 --> 00:20:50.527 line:80%
All I can do is gamble everything.

00:20:51.180 --> 00:20:52.500 line:80%
In this situation,

00:20:53.090 --> 00:20:54.660 line:80%
I shouldn't drag you in.

00:20:55.540 --> 00:20:56.420 line:80%
Zhao,

00:20:56.420 --> 00:20:57.260 line:80%
tomorrow morning,

00:20:57.660 --> 00:20:59.530 line:80%
leave with Song Yuzhi.

00:20:59.530 --> 00:21:00.370 line:80%
I came all this way.

00:21:00.370 --> 00:21:01.780 line:80%
How could I leave you alone?

00:21:01.940 --> 00:21:02.810 line:80%
But...

00:21:02.810 --> 00:21:03.613 line:80%
No buts.

00:21:03.624 --> 00:21:05.350 line:80%
At the very least,
we have to kill Nie Zhe.

00:21:05.810 --> 00:21:06.980 line:80%
Right now,

00:21:07.220 --> 00:21:09.050 line:80%
I'm extremely displeased with him too.

00:21:11.370 --> 00:21:12.370 line:80%
You won't regret it?

00:21:13.402 --> 00:21:14.696 line:80%
Why do you talk so much nonsense?

00:21:16.660 --> 00:21:17.700 line:80%
As a businesswoman,

00:21:17.980 --> 00:21:19.740 line:80%
keeping promises matters most.

00:22:33.700 --> 00:22:34.540 line:80%
Honey.

00:22:42.460 --> 00:22:43.500 line:80%
Mr. Nie is unwell.

00:22:43.980 --> 00:22:46.090 line:80%
The Chief has gone to the Lady.

00:22:49.130 --> 00:22:50.530 line:80%
She doesn't deserve to be the Lady.

00:22:50.740 --> 00:22:51.680 line:80%
Lady Sun, spare my life.

00:22:54.420 --> 00:22:55.260 line:80%
Lady Sun...

00:23:11.090 --> 00:23:12.780 line:80%
The Young Lord caught a chill.

00:23:13.290 --> 00:23:15.040 line:80%
Chief, you need not worry.

00:23:15.180 --> 00:23:16.890 line:80%
He must've caught a cold

00:23:16.890 --> 00:23:17.780 line:80%
in the garden that day.

00:23:23.610 --> 00:23:25.433 line:80%
Si'en will one day
take charge of the sect.

00:23:25.444 --> 00:23:27.210 line:80%
He can't stay indoors
studying all the time.

00:23:27.420 --> 00:23:29.020 line:80%
He needs to move around more.

00:23:29.290 --> 00:23:30.130 line:80%
Honey.

00:23:32.850 --> 00:23:33.980 line:80%
You're back so soon.

00:23:35.090 --> 00:23:36.050 line:80%
Mission accomplished.

00:23:36.500 --> 00:23:38.460 line:80%
I heard as soon as I entered

00:23:38.460 --> 00:23:39.780 line:80%
that Si'en was unwell.

00:23:39.780 --> 00:23:40.940 line:80%
I was worried,

00:23:40.940 --> 00:23:41.980 line:80%
so I hurried over to see

00:23:41.980 --> 00:23:43.420 line:80%
if there's anything I can help with.

00:23:45.980 --> 00:23:48.420 line:80%
You needn't put on an act here.

00:23:49.220 --> 00:23:51.700 line:80%
Si'en cannot bear your concern.

00:23:51.700 --> 00:23:52.540 line:80%
You...

00:23:56.460 --> 00:23:57.330 line:80%
Honey...

00:23:57.810 --> 00:23:58.940 line:80%
Since Si'en is fine,

00:23:59.370 --> 00:24:00.330 line:80%
let's go back first.

00:24:27.740 --> 00:24:28.926 line:80%
Dear, thanks for what you did.

00:24:30.050 --> 00:24:31.330 line:80%
This operation went so smoothly,

00:24:32.090 --> 00:24:33.570 line:80%
thanks to your efforts.

00:24:34.460 --> 00:24:35.370 line:80%
Honey, you flatter me.

00:24:35.810 --> 00:24:36.980 line:80%
As your wife,

00:24:36.980 --> 00:24:39.570 line:80%
it is my duty to share your burdens.

00:24:39.570 --> 00:24:40.740 line:80%
As long as you are pleased,

00:24:41.360 --> 00:24:42.220 line:80%
I am

00:24:42.220 --> 00:24:43.660 line:80%
fully content.

00:24:46.130 --> 00:24:46.970 line:80%
Mr. Yu,

00:24:47.610 --> 00:24:50.130 line:80%
reclaim the Qinglong
and Xuanwu Altars asap.

00:24:50.130 --> 00:24:52.220 line:80%
Leave the defense of Bliss Palace
to Fengge.

00:24:52.570 --> 00:24:53.570 line:80%
Understood.

00:24:55.460 --> 00:24:56.586 line:80%
Once Nie Zhe hears the news,

00:24:56.906 --> 00:24:58.090 line:80%
he will surely send Yu Huiyin

00:24:58.090 --> 00:24:59.890 line:80%
to retake the Qinglong
and Xuanwu Altars.

00:25:00.693 --> 00:25:02.379 line:80%
At that point,
the defense of Bliss Palace

00:25:02.740 --> 00:25:04.146 line:80%
can only be entrusted to Hu Fengge.

00:25:04.290 --> 00:25:06.530 line:80%
The red-clad woman
who captured me last time?

00:25:06.966 --> 00:25:08.180 line:80%
Hu Fengge is one of the orphans

00:25:08.191 --> 00:25:09.850 line:80%
Nie Hengcheng took into
the Demonic Camp.

00:25:09.850 --> 00:25:12.103 line:80%
She's known for exceptional talent
and ruthless methods.

00:25:12.460 --> 00:25:13.293 line:80%
After the great war,

00:25:13.304 --> 00:25:15.246 line:80%
Nie Hengcheng's followers
suffered heavy losses.

00:25:15.570 --> 00:25:17.610 line:80%
Hu Fengge was then promoted
to Elder Hufa.

00:25:18.370 --> 00:25:20.090 line:80%
She's always been loyal to Nie Zhe

00:25:20.460 --> 00:25:22.020 line:80%
and devoted to Yu Huiyin.

00:25:22.570 --> 00:25:24.050 line:80%
The remaining Camp elites

00:25:24.050 --> 00:25:25.180 line:80%
are all under her command.

00:25:25.666 --> 00:25:26.810 line:80%
If we clash with her head-on,

00:25:26.810 --> 00:25:28.240 line:80%
there will surely be a bitter battle.

00:25:28.251 --> 00:25:29.091 line:80%
There's no guarantee

00:25:29.168 --> 00:25:30.699 line:80%
Nie Zhe won't seize the chance to flee.

00:25:30.740 --> 00:25:32.460 line:80%
Once Nie Zhe leaves Bliss Palace,

00:25:32.460 --> 00:25:33.850 line:80%
it will be hard to catch him again.

00:25:34.220 --> 00:25:35.240 line:80%
Let's cut off his retreat.

00:25:35.500 --> 00:25:36.680 line:80%
Nail him inside Bliss Palace.

00:25:39.660 --> 00:25:40.500 line:80%
Shangguan,

00:25:40.700 --> 00:25:42.290 line:80%
lead men to Yaoyue Pass with Mr. Song

00:25:42.290 --> 00:25:44.700 line:80%
(Yaoyue Pass)
to draw Hu Fengge away.

00:25:50.740 --> 00:25:51.700 line:80%
Zhao and I will enter

00:25:52.370 --> 00:25:53.896 line:80%
from the back mountain of Bliss Palace.

00:25:54.056 --> 00:25:55.438 line:80%
There are many injured sect members

00:25:55.449 --> 00:25:56.700 line:80%
and villagers in Xuanwu Altar.

00:25:56.700 --> 00:25:57.806 line:80%
The enemy far outnumbers us.

00:25:58.290 --> 00:25:59.370 line:80%
If Yu Huiyin attacks,

00:25:59.370 --> 00:26:00.330 line:80%
how do we respond?

00:26:00.330 --> 00:26:01.170 line:80%
Don't worry.

00:26:01.340 --> 00:26:02.793 line:80%
The Young Master already has a plan.

00:26:37.980 --> 00:26:38.940 line:80%
You Guanyue,

00:26:39.660 --> 00:26:41.370 line:80%
where is your Young Master?

00:26:41.780 --> 00:26:42.620 line:80%
Could it be

00:26:43.980 --> 00:26:45.130 line:80%
that he's already dead?

00:26:47.090 --> 00:26:47.930 line:80%
Why don't you

00:26:49.130 --> 00:26:50.330 line:80%
come in and see

00:26:51.460 --> 00:26:52.330 line:80%
for yourself?

00:26:53.460 --> 00:26:54.820 line:80%
Yu Huiyin is naturally suspicious.

00:26:55.660 --> 00:26:57.500 line:80%
As long as we put on a show,

00:26:58.020 --> 00:26:59.370 line:80%
he will grow wary

00:26:59.850 --> 00:27:01.090 line:80%
and dare not act rashly.

00:27:03.020 --> 00:27:04.020 line:80%
Nie Zhe's end

00:27:05.420 --> 00:27:06.850 line:80%
should also be shown to my father.

00:27:28.850 --> 00:27:29.690 line:80%
Traitor!

00:27:40.130 --> 00:27:40.970 line:80%
Let's go.

00:28:03.780 --> 00:28:04.660 line:80%
Xuanwu Altar

00:28:05.370 --> 00:28:06.610 line:80%
isn't a place you can enter

00:28:07.020 --> 00:28:08.180 line:80%
just because you want to.

00:28:29.850 --> 00:28:30.810 line:80%
Come in, then.

00:28:33.940 --> 00:28:34.780 line:80%
Something's wrong.

00:28:34.940 --> 00:28:35.780 line:80%
Guards.

00:28:36.180 --> 00:28:37.020 line:80%
Yes.

00:28:37.780 --> 00:28:38.986 line:80%
Hurry and notify Bliss Palace.

00:28:39.220 --> 00:28:40.493 line:80%
Tell them to stay on high alert.

00:28:40.660 --> 00:28:41.500 line:80%
Yes.

00:28:48.460 --> 00:28:50.180 line:80%
Your contribution is outstanding.

00:28:50.460 --> 00:28:52.370 line:80%
You're worthy of being my wife.

00:28:52.850 --> 00:28:54.500 line:80%
After we finish the Mu clan remnants,

00:28:55.130 --> 00:28:56.850 line:80%
we shall hold the investiture ceremony.

00:28:58.610 --> 00:28:59.610 line:80%
Thank you, Chief.

00:29:07.740 --> 00:29:08.580 line:80%
Actually,

00:29:09.050 --> 00:29:11.180 line:80%
as long as I can stay by your side,

00:29:12.050 --> 00:29:13.810 line:80%
I will be fully content.

00:29:20.050 --> 00:29:20.940 line:80%
It's getting late.

00:29:21.780 --> 00:29:23.090 line:80%
Si'en needs to rest.

00:29:24.050 --> 00:29:26.180 line:80%
Why do you look unhappy?

00:29:29.220 --> 00:29:30.673 line:80%
Fellow disciples fighting each other.

00:29:31.130 --> 00:29:32.530 line:80%
What is there to be happy about?

00:29:35.780 --> 00:29:36.810 line:80%
Are you dissatisfied

00:29:36.810 --> 00:29:39.290 line:80%
with the Chief?

00:29:39.740 --> 00:29:42.130 line:80%
When my foster father was still alive,

00:29:42.460 --> 00:29:44.330 line:80%
we often drank wine in this hall.

00:29:44.610 --> 00:29:47.180 line:80%
Lu and Han would dance
with swords for amusement.

00:29:47.610 --> 00:29:49.180 line:80%
If Mr. Mu Zhengming came,

00:29:49.530 --> 00:29:50.980 line:80%
he'd play music in accompaniment.

00:29:51.570 --> 00:29:53.050 line:80%
Back then, the sect prospered.

00:29:53.420 --> 00:29:54.373 line:80%
Everyone was still here.

00:29:54.890 --> 00:29:56.330 line:80%
There was no rebellion to suppress

00:29:57.810 --> 00:29:58.810 line:80%
and certainly no

00:29:59.810 --> 00:30:01.370 line:80%
shamelessness,

00:30:01.370 --> 00:30:02.850 line:80%
no disregard for moral bonds.

00:30:08.050 --> 00:30:09.740 line:80%
That's not right.

00:30:10.610 --> 00:30:11.810 line:80%
Are you saying

00:30:12.180 --> 00:30:14.700 line:80%
the Chief is inferior
to the former chief?

00:30:15.460 --> 00:30:17.180 line:80%
After the former chief passed away,

00:30:17.180 --> 00:30:19.330 line:80%
the sect nearly fell apart.

00:30:19.330 --> 00:30:20.570 line:80%
If not for the Chief

00:30:20.570 --> 00:30:22.460 line:80%
turning the tide and restoring order,

00:30:22.880 --> 00:30:23.740 line:80%
how would the sect

00:30:23.740 --> 00:30:26.460 line:80%
enjoy today's prosperity and stability?

00:30:27.056 --> 00:30:29.130 line:80%
What right do you have
to speak of the former chief?

00:30:29.130 --> 00:30:30.583 line:80%
If my foster father were still alive,

00:30:30.890 --> 00:30:34.020 line:80%
how could he tolerate
a treacherous person like you?

00:30:35.130 --> 00:30:35.970 line:80%
You...

00:30:37.180 --> 00:30:38.020 line:80%
Enough.

00:30:39.660 --> 00:30:40.610 line:80%
Ruxin,

00:30:40.610 --> 00:30:41.810 line:80%
since Si'en is sleepy,

00:30:42.570 --> 00:30:43.890 line:80%
take him back to rest.

00:30:51.530 --> 00:30:52.370 line:80%
Let's go.

00:30:59.740 --> 00:31:00.700 line:80%
Chief,

00:31:02.500 --> 00:31:04.220 line:80%
look at Ruxin...

00:31:05.780 --> 00:31:07.780 line:80%
Servants, remove all of this.

00:31:08.890 --> 00:31:09.730 line:80%
Yes,

00:31:10.090 --> 00:31:10.930 line:80%
Chief.

00:31:32.700 --> 00:31:33.810 line:80%
You're not dead.

00:31:36.460 --> 00:31:37.420 line:80%
Uncle Nie.

00:31:38.780 --> 00:31:39.620 line:80%
Qingyan.

00:31:41.290 --> 00:31:42.130 line:80%
Lady Sun,

00:31:42.130 --> 00:31:44.020 line:80%
I didn't promise to spare your life.

00:31:44.420 --> 00:31:45.330 line:80%
I advise you

00:31:45.610 --> 00:31:47.130 line:80%
to mind your words and actions

00:31:47.130 --> 00:31:48.220 line:80%
and stop meddling.

00:31:48.660 --> 00:31:49.700 line:80%
Mu Qingyan,

00:31:50.610 --> 00:31:51.940 line:80%
what do you mean by this?

00:31:51.940 --> 00:31:53.700 line:80%
The capable rule the sect.

00:31:54.530 --> 00:31:55.810 line:80%
I wish to face you

00:31:56.370 --> 00:31:57.700 line:80%
in another duel.

00:31:59.700 --> 00:32:00.660 line:80%
Have you forgotten?

00:32:01.420 --> 00:32:03.420 line:80%
You already lost two years ago.

00:32:03.420 --> 00:32:05.980 line:80%
You also ate two years ago.
Why still eat today?

00:32:05.980 --> 00:32:07.700 line:80%
Besides, you poisoned him last time

00:32:07.700 --> 00:32:09.050 line:80%
and won without honor.

00:32:09.940 --> 00:32:11.700 line:80%
Even if you had won by strength,

00:32:12.370 --> 00:32:14.370 line:80%
does that mean
he can't challenge you again?

00:32:14.370 --> 00:32:15.210 line:80%
Mu Qingyan,

00:32:15.570 --> 00:32:17.850 line:80%
you sneaked into Bliss Palace

00:32:17.850 --> 00:32:20.290 line:80%
and let this demoness
spout nonsense here.

00:32:20.980 --> 00:32:22.740 line:80%
Are you planning to betray the sect?

00:32:22.740 --> 00:32:23.986 line:80%
The sect belongs to the Mu clan.

00:32:24.660 --> 00:32:25.733 line:80%
How can this be betrayal?

00:32:26.290 --> 00:32:27.130 line:80%
What?

00:32:27.370 --> 00:32:28.610 line:80%
Are you afraid?

00:32:41.740 --> 00:32:42.660 line:80%
Shangguan,

00:32:42.660 --> 00:32:43.530 line:80%
you traitor.

00:32:43.940 --> 00:32:46.330 line:80%
Elders Kaiyang and Yaoguang took you in.

00:32:47.180 --> 00:32:49.500 line:80%
They were loyal to the former chief.

00:32:49.500 --> 00:32:50.593 line:80%
Yet you switched allegiance

00:32:50.604 --> 00:32:51.570 line:80%
and betrayed the sect.

00:32:52.500 --> 00:32:53.740 line:80%
Elder Hu, that's not right.

00:32:54.130 --> 00:32:56.420 line:80%
From beginning to end,
I have only been loyal to Mr. Mu.

00:32:56.420 --> 00:32:57.403 line:80%
I have never changed.

00:32:57.414 --> 00:32:58.927 line:80%
Why accuse me of switching allegiance?

00:32:59.220 --> 00:33:00.295 line:80%
Back then, the two elders

00:33:00.306 --> 00:33:01.980 line:80%
wholeheartedly followed Nie Hengcheng.

00:33:02.370 --> 00:33:03.443 line:80%
They died without regret.

00:33:03.780 --> 00:33:04.940 line:80%
Today, I do the same.

00:33:05.220 --> 00:33:07.050 line:80%
You've always been Mu Qingyan's spy.

00:33:07.610 --> 00:33:08.450 line:80%
You deserve death.

00:33:09.780 --> 00:33:10.620 line:80%
(The summons.)

00:33:10.776 --> 00:33:12.216 line:80%
(Something's wrong at Bliss Palace.)

00:33:19.370 --> 00:33:20.290 line:80%
What's going on?

00:33:20.530 --> 00:33:21.370 line:80%
Numbing Powder.

00:33:22.090 --> 00:33:24.050 line:80%
You're a righteous sect member,

00:33:24.370 --> 00:33:25.610 line:80%
yet you play such petty tricks?

00:33:25.700 --> 00:33:26.740 line:80%
Necessity knows no rules.

00:33:27.153 --> 00:33:28.659 line:80%
A gentleman need not cling to trifles.

00:33:30.890 --> 00:33:32.420 line:80%
Victory matters more than origins.

00:33:33.610 --> 00:33:34.930 line:80%
Moves need not follow convention.

00:33:35.980 --> 00:33:36.820 line:80%
New knowledge.

00:34:08.850 --> 00:34:10.810 line:80%
Your cultivation improved so soon.

00:34:11.370 --> 00:34:12.810 line:80%
What have you practiced?

00:34:13.060 --> 00:34:14.060 line:80%
You've lost.

00:34:14.490 --> 00:34:15.370 line:80%
Uncle Nie,

00:34:16.330 --> 00:34:17.180 line:80%
step down.

00:34:29.180 --> 00:34:30.810 line:80%
Powder ground from Qianxun Wood.

00:34:32.330 --> 00:34:33.540 line:80%
It's said Qianxun Wood

00:34:33.540 --> 00:34:35.370 line:80%
can catalyze the poison
of Suzi Fragrance.

00:34:38.850 --> 00:34:41.540 line:80%
So, the poison you used on him
was Suzi Fragrance.

00:34:47.180 --> 00:34:48.140 line:80%
Hand over the antidote.

00:34:48.780 --> 00:34:49.646 line:80%
What antidote?

00:34:49.657 --> 00:34:50.877 line:80%
The antidote to Suzi Fragrance.

00:34:52.370 --> 00:34:54.323 line:80%
Mr. Mu originally thought
the poison he suffered

00:34:54.334 --> 00:34:55.330 line:80%
was from the Wudu Palm.

00:34:56.100 --> 00:34:57.330 line:80%
He never expected

00:34:57.330 --> 00:34:59.890 line:80%
the truly lethal poison to be...

00:35:02.100 --> 00:35:03.220 line:80%
So what?

00:35:05.140 --> 00:35:06.850 line:80%
You're sharp as a fox.

00:35:07.660 --> 00:35:09.740 line:80%
How could ordinary poisons fool you?

00:35:09.970 --> 00:35:11.930 line:80%
Suzi Fragrance is colorless
and odorless.

00:35:12.890 --> 00:35:15.490 line:80%
I meant to let it slowly
consume you to death.

00:35:17.410 --> 00:35:19.450 line:80%
Once mixed with Qianxun Wood,

00:35:19.450 --> 00:35:20.890 line:80%
it becomes deadly poison.

00:35:21.660 --> 00:35:23.220 line:80%
There is no cure in the world.

00:35:24.290 --> 00:35:25.130 line:80%
Mu Qingyan,

00:35:25.580 --> 00:35:27.010 line:80%
so what if you won?

00:35:28.700 --> 00:35:31.220 line:80%
Even your mother wants you dead.

00:35:32.010 --> 00:35:33.330 line:80%
Your mother tried to kill you.

00:35:33.890 --> 00:35:36.780 line:80%
Your father also died unnaturally
because of you.

00:35:37.220 --> 00:35:39.660 line:80%
What right do you have
to live in this world?

00:35:43.060 --> 00:35:43.930 line:80%
My father...

00:35:46.100 --> 00:35:47.620 line:80%
How exactly did he die?

00:35:53.540 --> 00:35:55.540 line:80%
After years of being consumed
by Suzi Fragrance,

00:35:56.370 --> 00:35:58.100 line:80%
the poison flared, and he died.

00:36:17.290 --> 00:36:19.100 line:80%
So, you did kill him...

00:36:26.970 --> 00:36:27.810 line:80%
Don't listen to them.

00:36:45.060 --> 00:36:46.930 line:80%
This cage is made of refined dark iron.

00:36:47.490 --> 00:36:48.620 line:80%
You cannot break it.

00:36:49.370 --> 00:36:50.370 line:80%
There will no longer be

00:36:50.810 --> 00:36:52.010 line:80%
a Mu clan in this world.

00:36:52.010 --> 00:36:53.740 line:80%
Nie Zhe, you shameless jerk.

00:36:53.740 --> 00:36:55.180 line:80%
How could you resort to dirty tricks?

00:36:55.180 --> 00:36:56.970 line:80%
Stop your futile struggle.

00:36:56.970 --> 00:36:59.780 line:80%
Soon, you'll become piles
of white bones.

00:37:08.970 --> 00:37:09.850 line:80%
Erosion Ants.

00:37:10.100 --> 00:37:11.970 line:80%
A paired mother-and-child Gu

00:37:12.220 --> 00:37:13.220 line:80%
recorded in strange lore.

00:37:13.220 --> 00:37:14.410 line:80%
They feed on flesh and blood

00:37:14.890 --> 00:37:16.060 line:80%
and reproduce rapidly.

00:37:17.780 --> 00:37:18.700 line:80%
They're getting closer.

00:37:18.780 --> 00:37:19.620 line:80%
Use your inner power.

00:37:25.660 --> 00:37:26.660 line:80%
Don't waste your effort.

00:37:27.140 --> 00:37:28.180 line:80%
Just wait for death.

00:37:28.850 --> 00:37:29.690 line:80%
Nie Zhe!

00:37:35.970 --> 00:37:37.543 line:80%
The child ants must sense the mother ant

00:37:37.554 --> 00:37:38.540 line:80%
to receive commands.

00:37:38.540 --> 00:37:40.060 line:80%
The one controlling the ants

00:37:40.060 --> 00:37:41.180 line:80%
must be nearby.

00:37:44.970 --> 00:37:46.140 line:80%
At a time like this,

00:37:47.330 --> 00:37:48.450 line:80%
why not come out?

00:37:49.060 --> 00:37:50.850 line:80%
If you can't witness
our miserable deaths,

00:37:51.580 --> 00:37:53.450 line:80%
wouldn't all your scheming be in vain?

00:37:53.890 --> 00:37:55.330 line:80%
You know who's behind this?

00:37:55.740 --> 00:37:56.740 line:80%
I miscalculated.

00:37:57.163 --> 00:37:59.309 line:80%
I didn't expect
that among Nie Hengcheng's disciples,

00:37:59.700 --> 00:38:01.330 line:80%
one would still be alive.

00:38:02.220 --> 00:38:03.700 line:80%
If I'm not mistaken,

00:38:05.140 --> 00:38:06.850 line:80%
it must be Han Yisu,

00:38:06.850 --> 00:38:07.970 line:80%
Elder Han, right?

00:38:14.720 --> 00:38:25.380 line:80%
=Generation to Generation=

00:38:44.140 --> 00:38:48.550 line:80%
♪The breeze is gentle,
and spring is fair♪

00:38:49.115 --> 00:38:53.730 line:80%
♪I roam the rivers and hills
in the martial world♪

00:38:54.070 --> 00:38:58.635 line:80%
♪With a shining cup,
I drink with delight tonight♪

00:38:59.160 --> 00:39:03.460 line:80%
♪Free to wander in the world♪

00:39:06.405 --> 00:39:11.105 line:80%
♪I drink with the breeze,
lost in my dreams♪

00:39:11.630 --> 00:39:15.920 line:80%
♪I rest beneath the stars' soft gleam♪

00:39:16.580 --> 00:39:20.610 line:80%
♪The night is calm, still as a stream♪

00:39:20.925 --> 00:39:26.050 line:80%
♪It washes away all judgment and scheme♪

00:39:26.625 --> 00:39:31.435 line:80%
♪I drink with the breeze,
lost in my dreams♪

00:39:31.650 --> 00:39:35.820 line:80%
♪I hold the bright moon
as I return home♪

00:39:36.545 --> 00:39:40.480 line:80%
♪I freely roam in the world♪

00:39:40.980 --> 00:39:46.255 line:80%
♪All I ask is that you go with me♪

00:40:08.985 --> 00:40:14.115 line:80%
♪I drink with the breeze,
lost in my dreams♪

00:40:14.480 --> 00:40:18.850 line:80%
♪I hold the bright moon
as I return home♪

00:40:19.115 --> 00:40:23.245 line:80%
♪I freely roam in the world♪

00:40:23.430 --> 00:40:29.005 line:80%
♪All I ask is that you go with me♪